980/flight-extras-baggage-ryanair-budget-costs"><div class="lazy-container"> <picture><source type="image/avif" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/285x190/1894980_1.avif" media="screen and (min-width: 1200px)"><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/285x190/1894980_1.webp" media="screen and (min-width: 1200px)"><source type="image/jpeg" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/285x190/1894980_1.jpg" media="screen and (min-width: 1200px)"><source type="image/avif" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/183x122/1894980_1.avif" media="screen and (min-width: 980px)"><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/183x122/1894980_1.webp" media="screen and (min-width: 980px)"><source type="image/jpeg" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/183x122/1894980_1.jpg" media="screen and (min-width: 980px)"><source type="image/avif" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/237x141/1894980_1.avif" media="screen and (max-width: 979px)"><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/237x141/1894980_1.webp" media="screen and (max-width: 979px)"><source type="image/jpeg" srcset="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/237x141/1894980_1.jpg" media="screen and (max-width: 979px)"><img src="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/183x122/1894980_1.jpg" alt="flight extras baggage ryanair budget costs" title="flight extras baggage ryanair budget costs" width="183" height="122" loading="lazy"></picture> <span class="bookmark-icon" data-bookmark="0" data-article-id="1894980" data-article-headline="Expert warns tourists to think twice before adding extras with popular budget airline" data-article-url="https://www.express.co.uk/travel/articles/1894980/flight-extras-baggage-ryanair-budget-costs" data-article-image="https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/25/285x169/1894980_1.jpg"> 